# From 18% to 100%: Full White-Label CRM+ERP Implementation Plan

**Baseline**: [walkthrough.md](file:///Users/utilisateur/.gemini/antigravity/brain/ec1ce6ed-29c4-4d81-b3c0-d6be709ebd81/walkthrough.md) · **Spec**: [report.md](file:///Users/utilisateur/Desktop/turbo-octo-robot/report.md) (787 lines, ~120 features)
**Current stack**: FastAPI 0.110 · SQLAlchemy 2.0 · Pydantic 2.6 · Python 3.10+ · Docker

---

## Architecture Decision: Standalone FastAPI Path

This plan commits to the **standalone expansion** path (not ERPNext migration). Rationale:
- Full control & modern async stack ✅
- True white-label capability (no Frappe branding) ✅
- API-first → any frontend can be plugged in ✅
- Trade-off accepted: longer build (~10-12 months) but vastly more flexible product

---

