## Timeline Overview

| Phase | Name | Duration | Weeks | Cumulative |
|:-----:|------|:--------:|:-----:|:----------:|
| 1 | Foundation & Architecture | 3 weeks | W1-3 | W3 |
| 2 | Deal Pipeline & CRM Completion | 4 weeks | W4-7 | W7 |
| 3 | Financial Engine (ERP Core) | 5 weeks | W4-8 | W8 |
| 4 | Project & Resource Management | 3 weeks | W9-11 | W11 |
| 5 | Workflow Automation | 3 weeks | W9-11 | W11 |
| 6 | Reporting & Business Intelligence | 3 weeks | W12-14 | W14 |
| 7 | HR & Operations | 2 weeks | W12-13 | W13 |
| 8 | Internationalization | 3 weeks | W14-16 | W16 |
| 9 | Frontend Web Application | 8 weeks | W17-24 | W24 |
| 10 | Mobile & Offline | 4 weeks | W25-28 | W28 |
| 11 | Integration Ecosystem | 3 weeks | W25-27 | W27 |
| 12 | White-Label & Security Hardening | 3 weeks | W29-31 | W31 |
| 13 | Launch Preparation | 3 weeks | W32-34 | W34 |
| | **Total** | | | **~34 weeks** |

> [!NOTE]
> Phases 2+3, 4+5, 6+7, and 10+11 run **in parallel** with separate developers. With 2 full-time developers the calendar time is ~34 weeks (~8 months). With 3-4 devs it compresses to ~6 months.

