```

#### [NEW] `standalone/app/services/forex.py`
- Automated rate feeds (ECB API, OpenExchangeRates)
- Historical rate lookup for any date
- Rate caching with configurable staleness threshold
- Currency conversion utility used by all financial modules

### 3.2 Chart of Accounts & General Ledger (Weeks 2-3)

#### [NEW] `standalone/app/models/accounting.py`
```python
class ChartOfAccounts  # Tenant-specific account structures
class Account          # Assets, Liabilities, Equity, Revenue, Expenses
class FiscalYear       # Period definitions
class FiscalPeriod     # Monthly/quarterly periods within fiscal year
class JournalEntry     # Header: date, memo, status, approval
class JournalEntryLine # Debit/Credit lines with account, amount, currency
class AccountBalance   # Denormalized running balances for performance
```

#### [NEW] `standalone/app/services/ledger.py`
- Double-entry enforcement (debits = credits per entry)
- Multi-currency journal entries with base currency conversion
- Period-end closing procedures
- Trial balance computation
- Account balance caching and reconciliation
- Immutable posted entries (append-only after posting)

### 3.3 Accounts Receivable & Invoicing (Week 3-4)

#### [NEW] `standalone/app/models/invoicing.py`
