- Tax calculation with configurable rules
- Payment matching and AR aging
- Dunning management (automated reminders via Celery)
- Revenue recognition (retainer spread, success fee on close, milestone-based)
- PDF invoice generation (ReportLab or WeasyPrint)

### 3.4 Accounts Payable (Week 4)

#### [NEW] `standalone/app/models/payables.py`
