## Phase 9: Frontend Web Application

**Goal**: Build a professional, financial-services-grade web application.
**Duration**: 8 weeks · **Priority**: 🔴 Critical
**Dependencies**: Phases 6 + 8 (all backend APIs complete)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Technology choice**: Next.js 15 + React 19 + Tailwind v4 (matching Alecia ecosystem standard). This ensures code reuse potential with existing Alecia projects.

### 9.1 Foundation (Week 1-2)

#### [NEW] `frontend/` — Next.js application
- Project scaffolding with TypeScript strict mode
- Design system: typography (Inter/Instrument Sans), color palette, spacing
- Component library: Button, Input, Select, Modal, Toast, Table, Card
- Layout system: sidebar navigation, breadcrumbs, command palette
- Auth flow: login, register, forgot password, MFA screen
- API client with request/response interceptors, error handling

### 9.2 CRM Views (Week 3-4)

- **Contacts**: List (table + filters), Detail view, Create/Edit forms
- **Companies**: List, Detail with org chart, financials summary
- **Deals**: Kanban pipeline board (drag-and-drop), Detail view, Timeline
- **Relationship Graph**: D3.js/Sigma.js network visualization
- **Communication Center**: Email inbox, thread view, template picker
- **Document Manager**: File browser, upload, version history, sharing UI

### 9.3 ERP Views (Week 5-6)

- **Chart of Accounts**: Tree view with drill-down
- **Journal Entries**: Create with multi-line debit/credit form, approval
- **Invoicing**: Invoice builder, payment recording, AR aging table
- **Expenses**: Submission form, receipt upload, approval queue
- **Reports**: P&L, Balance Sheet, Cash Flow with date range picker
- **Time Tracking**: Weekly grid entry, timer mode, approval

### 9.4 Dashboard & Analytics (Week 7)

- **Managing Partner Dashboard**: Revenue gauge, pipeline funnel, team grid
- **Deal Lead Dashboard**: Active deals cards, deadline calendar, team status
- **Custom Dashboard Builder**: Drag-and-drop widget placement
- **Charts**: Line, bar, pie, funnel (Recharts or Nivo)

### 9.5 Admin & Settings (Week 8)

- **Settings**: Tenant branding, deal stages, workflow editor
- **User Management**: Invite, role assignment, permissions matrix
- **Workflow Editor**: Visual state machine builder
- **Audit Log Viewer**: Searchable activity log
- **White-Label Settings**: Logo upload, color picker, custom domain

### Phase 9 Deliverables
- ✅ Professional financial-services-grade web UI
- ✅ Full CRM views with Kanban pipeline
- ✅ Complete ERP views with double-entry forms
- ✅ 4 role-optimized dashboards
- ✅ Admin panel with visual workflow builder

