## Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Financial engine complexity underestimated | Start accounting models in Phase 1 design review; hire domain expert reviewer |
| Frontend scope creep | Lock design mockups before coding; fixed feature set per release |
| Multi-tenancy data leaks | Automated tenant isolation tests; mandatory query scoping middleware |
| Performance at scale | Load test after each major phase, not just at end |
| Regulatory compliance gaps | Engage compliance consultant in Phase 12 |
